adius (film)|Radius]]''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Laci Kay]] \u2013 ''[[Broken Angels (2017 film)|Broken Angels]]'''''\n* Alessandra Panepinto \u2013 ''Check Point''\n* Alyssa Elle Steinacker \u2013 ''Cassidy Red''\n* Madison Mae \u2013 ''Girl Followed''\n|}\n\n=== Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film \u2013 Young Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film \u2013 Young Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Christopher Convery]] \u2013 ''[[Haters Back Off]]'''''\n* Armani Jackson \u2013 ''Little Boxes''\n* Grayson Thorne Kilpatrick \u2013 ''Bad Blood: The Movie''\n* Gunnar Goldberg \u2013 ''Casual''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Jolie Ledford]] \u2013 ''A Doggone Hollywood'''''\n* Adriana Shnayderman \u2013 ''Just Add Magic''\n* Brooklyn Robinson \u2013 ''Pineapple''\n* Chalet Lizette Brannan \u2013 ''Beach Massacre at Kill Devil Hills''\n* Emily Delahunty \u2013 ''Project Mc\u00b2''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film \u2013 Teen Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film \u2013 Teen Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Connor Muhl]] \u2013 ''[[Heartthrob (film)|Heartthrob]]'''''\n* Sean Ryan Fox \u2013 ''Christmas All Over Again''\n* Ticoon Kim \u2013 ''2nd Generation''\n* Trevor Larcom \u2013 ''Fuller House''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Isabella Bazler \u2013 ''[[Geo Disaster]]'''''\n* Hailey Kittle \u2013 ''2nd Generation''\n* Madeline Lupi \u2013 ''Messenger of Wrath''\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Best Performance in a Short Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Short Film \u2013 Young Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Perform