irchmore \u2013 ''I Believe in You: Michael Buble''\n* Nathan Blaiwes \u2013 ''Dancin With U''\n* Kacey Fifield \u2013 ''Hear me out''\n* Parker James Fullmore \u2013 ''Love Letters''\n* [[Prymrr]]- ''Never Give Up''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Dalton Cyr]] \u2013 ''Breathe'''''\n* Laci Kay \u2013 ''Rejected''\n* Max and Mango \u2013 ''Capitaine Abandonne''\n* Hunter Payton \u2013 ''Dario: Point of no Return''\n|}\n\n=== Best Performance in a TV Commercial ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\"|Best Performance in a TV Commercial \u2013 Young Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\"|Best Performance in a TV Commercial \u2013 Young Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Brock Brenner \u2013  ''King's Hawaiian Bread: Super Bowl Li'''''\n* Luke Roessler \u2013 ''The Robot''\n* Liam MacDonald \u2013 ''PS4: Star Wars Battlefront II \u2013 Rivalry''\n* T.K. Weaver  \u2013 ''Subaru Impreza: Moving Out''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Ai-Chan Carrier \u2013 ''Kevin Hart: Demystifying Premiums'''''\n|}\n\n=== Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role \u2013 Young Artist\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role \u2013 Teen Artist\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Nicholas Fry \u2013 ''[[Max & Ruby]]'''''\n* Bria D. Singleton \u2013 ''All I Want for Christmas Is You''\n* Ciara Alexys \u2013 ''Luna Petunia: Return to Amazia''\n* Mila Brener \u2013 ''Shimmer and Shine''\n* Saara Chaudry \u2013 ''The Breadwinner''\n* Lucas Kalechstein \u2013 ''Top Wing''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Dogen Eyeler \u2013 ''[[PAW Patrol]]'''''\n* [[Rachelle Henry]] \u2013 ''Beast''\n* Hannah Swain \u2013 ''Ruff-Ruff Tweet and Dave''\n* Kate Scott \u2013 ''Suspense''\n|}\n\n=== Best New Media Performance ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best New Media Performance \u2013 Young Artist\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best New Media Performance \u2013 Teen Artist\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Bryson Robinson \u2013 ''[[Mani (web series)|Mani]]'''''\n* Juju Journey Brener \u2013 ''AOK''\n* Brianni Walker \u2013 ''[[Mani (web series)|Mani]]''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Mathew Edmondson ]] \u2013 ''Coming Distractions'''''\n* Walker Satterwhite \u2013 ''Day 5''\n* Sheridan Archbold \u2013 ''Making It Again?''\n* Rainni Moran \u2013 ''Or So the Story Goes''\n* Skylar Radzion \u2013 ''Super Drycleaners''\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Per [[WP:ELMINOFFICIAL]], choose one official website only -->\n*{{Official website|http://www.youngartistawards.org/}}\n\n{{Young Artist Awards}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Young Artist Awards, 039}}\n[[Category:Young Artist Awards ceremonies]]\n[[Category:July 2018 events in the United States]]\n[[Category:2018 in California]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox film awards\n| number           = 39\n| award            = Young Artist Awards\n| award_link       = Young Artist Award\n| image            = Young Artist Award.jpg\n| image_size       = 100px\n| caption          =\n| alt              =\n| date             = July 14, 2018\n| site             = [[South Park Theatre]]<br />[[Los Angeles, California]]\n| awarded_for      = Achievement during the year [[2017 in film]] and [[2017 in television|television]]\n| host             = [[Liz Fuller]] and [[Petri Hawkins-Byrd]]\n| website          = [http://www.youngartistawards.org/ YoungArtistAwards.org]\n| last             = 38th\n| next             = 40th\n}}\n\nThe '''39th Young Artist Awards''' ceremony, presented by the [[Young Artist Association]], honored excellence of young performers between the ages of 5 to 18 in the fields of film, television, theatre and the internet for the 2017 calendar year. Winners were announced on July 14, 2018, at the annual ceremony held at the South Park Theatre in [[Los Angeles, California]].<ref name=\"YAA2018\">{{cite web|title=Nominees \u2013 Young Artist Awards|url=https://youngartistawards.org/2018winners|website=[[Young Artist Awards]]|date=July 14, 2018|}}</ref>\n\n{{TOC limit|3}}\n\n== \tWinners and nominees ==\n\u2605 '''Winners''' were announced on July 14, 2018.<ref name=\"YAA2018\" />\n\n=== 2018 Icon Award ===\n[[Jerry Mathers]]\n\n=== 2018 Inspiration to Youth Award ===\nMerrick Hanna\n\n=== 2018 Humanitarian Award ===\nChalet Lizette Brannan\n\n=== Best Performance in a Feature Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|[[Young Artist Award for Best Leading Young Actor in a Feature Film|Best Performance in a Feature Film \u2013 Leading Young Actor]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|[[Young Artist Award for Best Leading Young Actress in a Feature Film|Best Performance in a Feature Film \u2013 Leading Young Actress]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Jacob Tremblay]] \u2013 ''[[Wonder (film)|Wonder]]'''''\n* [[Oakes Fegley]] \u2013 ''[[Wonderstruck (film)|Wonderstruck]]''\n\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Savannah Liles \u2013 ''[[Prodigy (2017 film)|Prodigy]]'''''\n* Kelea Skelton \u2013 ''Monday Nights at Seven''\n* [[Brooklynn Prince]] \u2013 ''[[The Florida Project]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Feature Film \u2013 Leading Teen Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Feature Film \u2013 Leading Teen Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Carson Reaume]] \u2013 ''[[The Shack (2017 film)|The Shack]]'''''\n* Hunter Fischer \u2013 ''[[Hickok (film)|Hickok]]''\n* [[Noah Jupe]] \u2013 ''[[Suburbicon]]''\n\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Alyssa Elle Steinacker]] \u2013 ''[[Don't Come Back from the Moon]]'''''\n* Alexia Rosinski \u2013 ''Lost Fare''\n* [[Millicent Simmonds]] \u2013 ''[[Wonderstruck (film)|Wonderstruck]]''\n|-\n! style