oper]] \u2013 ''[[Prison Break]]'''''\n* Isaak Bailey \u2013 ''Rick Mercer Report''\n* Jailen Bates \u2013 ''[[Superior Donuts]]''\n* Jet Jurgensmeyer \u2013 ''[[Will & Grace]]''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Aubrey Fitzgerald \u2013 ''[[Training Day]]'''''\n* Charlie Boyle \u2013 ''[[The Mist]]''\n* Imogen Tear \u2013 ''[[The Magicians]]''\n* Juju Journey Brener \u2013 ''Your Son Has Been Kidnapped''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Guest Starring Teen Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Guest Starring Teen Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Sloane Morgan Siegel]] \u2013 ''Pure Genius'''''\n* Brendan Heard \u2013 ''Raising Expectations''\n* Joey Cipriano \u2013 ''[[Chicago Med]]''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Bridget McGarry]] \u2013 ''[[Blindspot (TV series)|Blindspot]]'''''\n* Brighton Sharbino \u2013 ''Law & Order: Special Victims Unit\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Recurring Young Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Recurring Young Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[TK Weaver]] \u2013 ''[[General Hospital]]'''''\n* Kai Wener \u2013 ''The Orville''\n* Keith L. Williams \u2013 ''[[The Last Man on Earth]]''\n* Tyler Mazzei \u2013 ''Outcast''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Ava Telek]] \u2013 ''The Magicians'''''\n* Arista Arhin \u2013 ''[[Star Trek: Discovery]]''\n* Ava Grace Cooper \u2013 ''[[When Calls the Heart]]''\n* Eva Ariel Binder \u2013 ''[[Grey's Anatomy]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Recurring Teen Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a TV Series \u2013 Recurring Teen Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Karim Fahmy]] \u2013 ''[[Prison Break]]'''''\n* Jordan Poole \u2013 ''Mr. D''\n* Max Steinberg \u2013 ''Max TV''\n* Tyler Huth \u2013 ''Manhunt: Unabomber''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Ava Frye]] \u2013 ''[[iZombie]]'''''\n* Ashlyn Boots \u2013 ''[[School of Rock]]''\n* Casey Burke \u2013 ''[[The Middle]]''\n* LuLu Lambros \u2013 ''[[Stuck in the Middle]]''\n* Stephanie Katherine Grant \u2013 ''[[The Goldbergs]]''\n|}\n\n=== Best Performance in a Music Video ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Music Video \u2013 Young Artist\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Music Video \u2013 Teen Artist\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Tim Luca Schmidt]] \u2013 ''Zu Hause \u2013 ESTA feat. Eric Philippi'''''\n* Maximus Birchmore \u2013 ''I Believe in You: Michael Buble''\n* Nathan Blaiwes \u2013 ''Dancin With U''\n* Kacey Fifield \u2013 ''Hear me out''\n* Parker James Fullmore \u2013 ''Love Letters''\n* [[Prymrr]]- ''Never Give Up''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Dalton Cyr]] \u2013 ''Breathe'''''\n* Laci Kay \u2013 ''Rejected''\n* Max and Mango \u2013 ''Capitaine Abandonne''\n* Hunter Payton \u2013 ''Dario: Point of no Return''\n|}\n\n=== Best Performance in a TV Commercial ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\"|Best Performance in a TV Commercial \u2013 Young Actor\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82;\"|Best Performance in a TV Commercial \u2013 Young Actress\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Brock Brenner \u2013  ''King's Hawaiian Bread: Super Bowl Li'''''\n* Luke Roessler \u2013 ''The Robot''\n* Liam MacDonald \u2013 PS4: Star Wars Battlefront II \u2013 Rivalry''\n* T.K. Weaver  \u2013 ''Subaru Impreza: Moving Out''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Ai-Chan Carrier \u2013 ''Kevin Hart: Demystifying Premiums'''''\n|}\n\n=== Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role \u2013 Young Artist\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best Performance in a Voice-Over Role \u2013 Teen Artist\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Nicholas Fry \u2013 ''[[Max & Ruby]]'''''\n* Bria D. Singleton \u2013 ''All I Want for Christmas Is You''\n* Ciara Alexys \u2013 ''Luna Petunia: Return to Amazia''\n* Mila Brener \u2013 ''Shimmer and Shine''\n* Saara Chaudry \u2013 ''The Breadwinner''\n* Lucas Kalechstein \u2013 ''Top Wing''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Dogen Eyeler \u2013 ''[[PAW Patrol]]'''''\n* [[Rachelle Henry]] \u2013 ''Beast''\n* Hannah Swain \u2013 ''Ruff-Ruff Tweet and Dave''\n* Kate Scott \u2013 ''Suspense''\n|}\n\n=== Best New Media Performance ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best New Media Performance \u2013 Young Artist\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82; width:50%;\"|Best New Media Performance \u2013 Teen Artist\n|-\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 Bryson Robinson \u2013 ''[[Mani (web series)|Mani]]'''''\n* Juju Journey Brener \u2013 ''AOK''\n* Brianni Walker \u2013 ''[[Mani]]''\n| valign=\"top\"|\n'''\u2605 [[Mathew Edmondson ]] \u2013 ''Coming Distractions'''''\n* Walker Satterwhite \u2013 ''Day 5''\n* Sheridan Archbold \u2013 ''Making It Again?''\n* Rainni Moran \u2013 ''Or So the Story Goes''\n* Skylar Radzion \u2013 ''Super Drycleaners''\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Per [[WP:ELMINOFFICIAL]], choose one official website only -->\n*{{Official website|http://www.youngartistawards.org/}}\n\n{{Young Artist Awards}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Young Artist Awards, 039}}\n[[Category:Young Artist Awards ceremonies]]\n[[Category:July 2018 events in the United States]]\n[[Category:2018 in California]]\n", "name_user": "GoingBatty", "label": "safe", "comment": "v2.02 - Repaired 8 links to disambiguation pages -(You can help)-American Crime,Mani,Stuck in the Middle,The Goldbergs,The Last Man on Earth,The Magicians,The Middle,The Mist, 1 to be fixed -Heartland/WP:WCWproject (Missing end bold/italic